Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 天亮了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…我因为要去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉你会不会有时候 希望我们一起出去吃个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司会开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 会的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我帮你再添一点喝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.41,0:04:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对对对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抹布 抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊 药草都用完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 司喜欢的那个墨角兰茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要再去买了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么工作结束后去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…我们一起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到没看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不觉得刚刚这两个人好像正要牵手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别那么招摇好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好像在生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过话说回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得自己实在太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我居然没能听到艾拉拉惊人的告白台词
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉拉能不能在我面前再向司司告白一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这辈子唯一的请求了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好嘛 好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没看到艾拉很困扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老实说艾拉的做法并不是什么值得赞扬的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是工作时间居然去告白什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满嘴上虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是昨晚一个人神魂颠倒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「我也好想那样浪漫的告白」什么什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 不对不是想告白而是想被告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}满满早晚也会遇到你的白马王子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs38}你一定是在嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早啊 两位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨晚睡得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是根本没怎么睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在说…说…说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们连K…K…KISS都还没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那一定是度过了一个苦闷的夜晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}康孝 这种玩笑太恶劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们俩已经是公司内部公认的一对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才要捉弄一下才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司和艾拉都不要理他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是正经啊 不愧是我亲爱的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说司 有件重要的事要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和恋人顺利发展的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是要不时的用心制造惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊喜…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没错 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}女生都会期盼着浪漫的惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想体验做公主的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司 可别太当真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然你这么说 其实雪莉你也在期待着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉 我能问个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要怎样才能喜欢上自己的搭档啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜欢什么的…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:08:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}矮油 听上去好像雪莉不喜欢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连上班都迟到的搭档怎么喜欢的起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 和营业部翔子酱约会的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种时候倒是很守时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们稍微谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们俩要好好的发展哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊喜 惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘀咕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早！安！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香月只是在吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原谅她吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小艾拉 麻烦泡杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也是夫人亲手做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她帮你做便当 你开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}内人还会考虑营养平衡的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已经十几年没人帮我做便当了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦呀？哦呀哦呀哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道小艾拉想帮司做便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这这这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且我一次都没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让满教你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙很会做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊喜！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能让女生高兴的惊喜到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然还是花束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是之前不是失败过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从背后顶膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那哪是惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是捉弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带她去吃豪华晚餐怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她好像对吃的没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做鬼脸怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很擅长做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是说了是让女生高兴的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉很擅长做鬼脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很恶心的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恶心啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样 还是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}或者……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在的司也很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看起来很幸福就够了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找我秘密商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道和司有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 正好我也有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实际上和恋人一起生活是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成为恋…恋…恋人前后 有什么不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 难道昨天已经K…K…KISS了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊不不不不 这太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们一直都住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和普通情侣比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进展快速也没什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说晚上也睡在同一个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道不只亲亲 还有更进一步的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知为什么 成为恋人后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能像以前那样顺畅的交流了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看你的样子 大概也能想象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以想请你教我做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来如此 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想做给那家伙吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想让他高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后想着就能像以前那样愉快的交谈了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是精神可嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吧 我来教你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那你想做什么样的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想啊 你要根据司的喜好来决定做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦… 司喜欢吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你问我 我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然连这种事情都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我真是不配做他的女朋友
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}午休不是早就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉说有事情要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}错误 没有听清楚  请再说一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fs38}都到现在了你还害羞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…到底发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉说要为你做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以你想吃什么就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要维持好恋人关系的秘诀就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时刻要准备着惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这难道是 艾拉给我准备的惊喜！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉的心意我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是如果只是单方面的被给予
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会很不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今早说的那个事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也只是想和艾拉吃个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那如果两个人一起做饭就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看来已经得出结论了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样的话 我还是不帮忙比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只会妨碍你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说这样的眉目传情地秀恩爱 还是回宿舍里去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以真是受不了这些外行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明明很感兴趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你刚才说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没什么啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才说到的做饭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想和你一起做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么样呢 司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然了 要不今晚就试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好想知道司喜欢吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 喜欢吃的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 蛋包饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像小孩子一样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司是我正式的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是接替香月的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没关系 我大概明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}惊喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你有什么烦心事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想若是要给喜欢的人一个惊喜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么样的才能让她高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想要让艾拉高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你太好懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「和喜欢的人度过的时光 才是最开心的」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉是这么和我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我也觉得也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说不管是你还是老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨拙的男性真是多呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事 有什么要我帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有的话就跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还算是没走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要把我当空气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太阳下山越来越晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司我想买睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？ 以前是因为没有才那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}之前一直觉得不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 要买情侣装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…倒不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饿了 但是饿着肚子会觉得饭特别好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗 真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们… 成为恋人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我好像都没有为艾拉做过什么特别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想过许多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是不知道怎样才能让艾拉高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只要你像原来那样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像原来那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要和司在一起就会很特别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是现在 我心情也是小鹿乱撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}心脏好像要爆裂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在那片光芒下 是不是也有各式各样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像平常一样生活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我是不是也是其中之一呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们现在这样才是特别的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外观好微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得第一次做成这样已经很不错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来画上喜欢的图案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明不用划掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}害羞到连我自己都看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是有点太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}艾拉也吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 你又开始写日记了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会笑我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不会笑你的
